platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Whether you’re a local or just visiting, music fans needn’t gamble on securing tickets to the hottest concerts and festivals in the UK. From monster headliners at London’s O2 Arena to an up-and-coming songstress at a corner club, Dice connects fans to their favorite musical acts with a slick, beautiful app that makes booking tickets a snap—and without additional fees. Sold-out show? Just hop on the waiting list and get an alert if tickets become available.
